section.section:
In Washington County this section:
Does not apply to any Class A, Class B, Class C, Class D, and any special Sunday license from the hours of 12 noon to 12 midnight;
Does not apply to Sunday sales when New Year's Eve or New Year's Day falls on a Sunday which is governed by § 11-402(w) of this article;
Provides that licensees selling alcoholic beverages on Sunday, except for holders of Class A light wine licenses for wineries, shall pay an annual fee of $250 in addition to their annual license fee; and
Provides that licensees may purchase a 1 day on-sale license for Sunday sale of alcoholic beverages when New Year's Eve falls on a Sunday. The licensee shall pay a $50 fee in addition to any other annual license fee.
